data.actual_result: Unsaved changes popup doesn't disappear when the role is moved back to the original spot
data.expected_result: Unsaved changes popup disappears when the role is moved back to the original spot
data.short_description: Moving a role to a different spot and back to the same spot shows unsaved changes
data.steps_to_repro: - Go to a server where you can manage roles that has at least 3/4 roles - Move one of the roles to a different spot in the list in server settings - Move the role back to the spot it was in before - Observe the unsaved changes popup
